// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <callExp> => Exp
//  <cast exp> => Exp
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp6> => Exp
//  <exp7> => Exp
//  <exp8> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <exp>? => Exp
//  <expList> => ExpList
//  <expList>? => ExpList
//  <for> => Statement
//  <forHelper1> => Statement
//  <forHelper1>? => Statement
//  <forHelper2> => Statement
//  <forHelper2>? => Statement
//  <if> => Statement
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <program> => Program
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  <unary exp> => Exp
//  <while> => Statement
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 7: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 8: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 9: <type> ::= `int
// 10: <type> ::= `boolean
// 11: <type> ::= ID
// 12: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 13: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 14: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 15: <stmt> ::= `;
// 16: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 17: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 18: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 19: <stmt> ::= <if>
// 20: <stmt> ::= <while>
// 21: <stmt> ::= <callExp> `;
// 22: <if> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 23: <if> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 24: <while> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= <for>
// 26: <forHelper1> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 27: <forHelper1> ::= <assign>
// 28: <forHelper1> ::= <callExp>
// 29: <forHelper2> ::= <assign>
// 30: <forHelper2> ::= <callExp>
// 31: <for> ::= `for `( <forHelper1>? $$0
// 32: <for> ::= `for `( $$0
// 33: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 34: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 35: <assign> ::= `++ ID
// 36: <assign> ::= `-- ID
// 37: <assign> ::= ID `++
// 38: <assign> ::= ID `--
// 39: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 40: <exp> ::= <exp> `|| <exp2>
// 41: <exp> ::= <exp2>
// 42: <exp2> ::= <exp2> `&& <exp3>
// 43: <exp2> ::= <exp3>
// 44: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `!= <exp4>
// 45: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `== <exp4>
// 46: <exp3> ::= <exp4>
// 47: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `< <exp5>
// 48: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `> <exp5>
// 49: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `<= <exp5>
// 50: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `>= <exp5>
// 51: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `instanceof ID
// 52: <exp4> ::= <exp5>
// 53: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `+ <exp6>
// 54: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `- <exp6>
// 55: <exp5> ::= <exp6>
// 56: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `* <exp7>
// 57: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `/ <exp7>
// 58: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `% <exp7>
// 59: <exp6> ::= <exp7>
// 60: <exp7> ::= <cast exp>
// 61: <exp7> ::= <unary exp>
// 62: <cast exp> ::= `( <type> `) <cast exp>
// 63: <cast exp> ::= `( <type> `) <exp8>
// 64: <unary exp> ::= `- <unary exp>
// 65: <unary exp> ::= `+ <unary exp>
// 66: <unary exp> ::= `! <unary exp>
// 67: <unary exp> ::= <exp8>
// 68: <exp8> ::= ID
// 69: <exp8> ::= <exp8> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 70: <exp8> ::= INTLIT
// 71: <exp8> ::= STRINGLIT
// 72: <exp8> ::= CHARLIT
// 73: <exp8> ::= `false
// 74: <exp8> ::= `true
// 75: <exp8> ::= `null
// 76: <exp8> ::= `this
// 77: <exp8> ::= <exp8> `. ID
// 78: <exp8> ::= `new ID `( `)
// 79: <exp8> ::= `( <exp8> `)
// 80: <exp8> ::= <callExp>
// 81: <callExp> ::= <exp8> `. ID `( <expList>? `)
// 82: <callExp> ::= <exp8> `. ID `( `)
// 83: <callExp> ::= ID `( <expList>? `)
// 84: <callExp> ::= ID `( `)
// 85: <callExp> ::= `super `. ID `( <expList>? `)
// 86: <callExp> ::= `super `. ID `( `)
// 87: <expList> ::= <exp>
// 88: <expList> ::= <exp> `, <expList>
// 89: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 90: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 91: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 92: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 93: any ::= {0..127}
// 94: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 95: ws ::= " "
// 96: ws ::= {10}
// 97: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 98: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 99: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 100: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 101: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 102: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 103: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 104: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 105: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 106: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 107: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 108: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 109: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 110: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 111: `for ::= "#" "f" "o" ws*
// 112: `for ::= "#" "f" "o"
// 113: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 114: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 115: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 116: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 117: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 118: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 119: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 120: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 121: `super ::= "#" "s" "u" ws*
// 122: `super ::= "#" "s" "u"
// 123: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 124: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 125: `instanceof ::= "#" "i" "n" ws*
// 126: `instanceof ::= "#" "i" "n"
// 127: `new ::= "#" "n" "e" ws*
// 128: `new ::= "#" "n" "e"
// 129: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 130: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 131: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 132: `! ::= "!"
// 133: `!= ::= "@" "!" ws*
// 134: `!= ::= "@" "!"
// 135: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 136: `% ::= "%"
// 137: `&& ::= "@" "&" ws*
// 138: `&& ::= "@" "&"
// 139: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 140: `* ::= "*"
// 141: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 142: `( ::= "("
// 143: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 144: `) ::= ")"
// 145: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 146: `{ ::= "{"
// 147: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 148: `} ::= "}"
// 149: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 150: `- ::= "-"
// 151: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 152: `+ ::= "+"
// 153: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 154: `= ::= "="
// 155: `== ::= "@" "=" ws*
// 156: `== ::= "@" "="
// 157: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 158: `[ ::= "["
// 159: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 160: `] ::= "]"
// 161: `|| ::= "@" "|" ws*
// 162: `|| ::= "@" "|"
// 163: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 164: `< ::= "<"
// 165: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 166: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 167: `, ::= "," ws*
// 168: `, ::= ","
// 169: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 170: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 171: `>= ::= "@" ">" ws*
// 172: `>= ::= "@" ">"
// 173: `. ::= "." ws*
// 174: `. ::= "."
// 175: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 176: `; ::= ";"
// 177: `++ ::= "@" "+" ws*
// 178: `++ ::= "@" "+"
// 179: `-- ::= "@" "-" ws*
// 180: `-- ::= "@" "-"
// 181: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 182: `/ ::= "/"
// 183: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 184: ID ::= letter128
// 185: ID ::= letter idChar* $$1
// 186: ID ::= letter $$1
// 187: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$2
// 188: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$2
// 189: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 190: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 191: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$3
// 192: INTLIT ::= "0" $$3
// 193: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 194: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 195: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$4
// 196: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$4
// 197: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 198: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 199: idChar ::= letter
// 200: idChar ::= digit
// 201: idChar ::= "_"
// 202: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 203: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 204: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 205: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 206: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 207: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 208: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 209: <forHelper1>? ::= <forHelper1>
// 210: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 211: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 212: <exp>? ::= <exp>
// 213: any* ::= any* any
// 214: any* ::= any
// 215: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 216: ws* ::= ws
// 217: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 218: digit* ::= digit
// 219: <expList>? ::= <expList>
// 220: <forHelper2>? ::= <forHelper2>
// 221: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit

// 223: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 224: idChar* ::= idChar

// 227: $$0 ::= `; <exp>? $$5
// 228: $$0 ::= `; $$5
// 229: $$1 ::= idChar128 ws*

// 236: $$4 ::= any128

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 318
        "#" => shift: 142
        ws => shift: 585
        <program> => shift: 24
        `class => shift: 139
        <start> => shift: 544
        ws* => shift: 645
        {10} => shift: 74
        " " => shift: 178
        <class decl> => shift: 655

**** STATE 2 ****
    digit128 ::= {176..185} !<empty bracket pair> <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    digit128 ::= {176..185} <%> // $$0
    digit128 ::= {176..185} <%> // $$5
    digit128 ::= {176..185} <%> // <empty bracket pair>

**** STATE 3 ****
    ID ::= letter128 <!!<empty bracket pair>%> ws* !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    ID ::= letter128 <!!<empty bracket pair>%> ws* // $$0
    ID ::= letter128 <!!<empty bracket pair>%> ws* // $$5

    ID ::= letter128 <!!<empty bracket pair>%> ws* // `||

    ID ::= letter128 [ws*] <!!<empty bracket pair>%> // $$5
    ID ::= letter128 [ws*] <!!<empty bracket pair>%> // <empty bracket pair>

        {176..185} => shift: 2
        {"1".."9"} => shift: 180
        <exp>? => shift: 195
        STRINGLIT => shift: 11
        letter128 => shift: 297
        "-" => shift: 242
        `; => shift: 407
        "!" => shift: 391
